{
  "id": "RAW_d0611a4e",
  "title": "破解大模型「无效并行推理」：Parallel-Probe 问世，并行推理效率提升 35.8%",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA3MzI4MjgzMw==&mid=2651020334&idx=4&sn=57c302ec4b9d4508864e8d799bf1038c",
  "date": "2026-03-07 04:18:00",
  "author": "机器之心",
  "siteName": "机器之心",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=08e6bc43&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F5L8bhP5dIqFlp2RMoYRC8ImwDgxGb6hq71hF7lbMiccibdKt9zxcdXEdF20GcccicWhEuyoyY3sRUwdvgibUnUYJFXQthNZ9XtdNVNmDT2YE1lc%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\" style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"><span></span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"4\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">当大模型推理进入&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">Parallel Thinking</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;时代，一个关键问题随之出现：</span></span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"4\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">模型在并行推理的过程中，究竟发生了什么？</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">多条推理路径同时展开，看似为模型带来了更强的能力，却也引入了一个长期被忽视的问题——</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">大量计算是否正在被浪费在已经「没有必要继续」的思考上？</span></span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"5\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">为了回答这一问题，来自马里兰大学、圣路易斯华盛顿大学、北卡罗来纳大学教堂山分校等机构的研究团队提出了&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">Parallel-Probe</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。不同于直接从算法设计出发，该研究首先通过引入</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;2D Probing</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，对 online 并行推理过程中的</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">全局动态性进行了系统性刻画。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">研究发现，并行推理并非一个「算得越多越好」的过程：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">全局共识往往在所有分支结束之前就已提前稳定，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">而少数冗长的长尾路径却持续占据大量计算资源，成为并行推理效率的主要瓶颈。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"6\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">基于这些关键发现，研究团队进一步提出了一个 training-free 的并行推理控制算法 Parallel-Probe，能够在不牺牲核心准确率的前提下，显著减少无效计算，将推理延迟降低</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;35.8%</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，总 token 成本降低&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">25.8%</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-height=\"372\" data-imgfileid=\"503535788\" data-ratio=\"0.27314814814814814\" data-width=\"1364\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=415fb1c1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F5L8bhP5dIqHhzp6bs52qckuxwb5uRK2fiaAa8gKz8AL1tfiaBTaIv3DzCX4ibI6KmE1yvz6qXa4r2Sh2DmpKz7bLTCPPnWu8RQJRmDWcGWWhIo%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p data-path-to-node=\"7\" style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">论文名称：Parallel-Probe: Towards Efficient Parallel Thinking via 2D Probing</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-path-to-node=\"7\" style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">论文链接：</span></span>\n     <response-element ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\">\n      <link-block><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\"><a href=\"https://arxiv.org/pdf/2602.03845\" target=\"_blank\">https://arxiv.org/pdf/2602.03845</a></span></span></link-block>\n     </response-element></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-path-to-node=\"7\" style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">Code：</span></span>\n     <response-element ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\">\n      <link-block><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\"><a href=\"https://github.com/zhengkid/Parallel-Probe\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/zhengkid/Parallel-Probe</a></span></span></link-block>\n     </response-element></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-path-to-node=\"7\" style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">Online Judge：</span></span>\n     <response-element ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\">\n      <link-block><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\"><a href=\"https://huggingface.co/spaces/EfficientReasoning/efficient_reasoning_online_judgement\" target=\"_blank\">https://huggingface.co/spaces/EfficientReasoning/efficient_reasoning_online_judgement</a></span></span></link-block>\n     </response-element></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"7\" style=\"text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <response-element ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\">\n    <link-block></link-block>\n   </response-element>\n  </p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"8\" style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><b data-path-to-node=\"8\" data-index-in-node=\"0\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">核心痛点：孤立的</span></span></b></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"8\" style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><b data-path-to-node=\"8\" data-index-in-node=\"0\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">「并行路径」到底带来了什么？</span></span></b></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"8\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">目前的并行推理方法（如多数投票机制）存在一个显著缺陷：各推理分支彼此独立。这意味着，即使大部分分支已经达成了共识，系统仍需等待所有分支（包括那些冗余的长尾路径）全部生成完毕。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-height=\"960\" data-imgfileid=\"503535789\" data-ratio=\"0.6111111111111112\" data-width=\"1570\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=647f70b4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F5L8bhP5dIqHdLanJkCAoL0PXnn1Wh3hHYUKPrqaCasHpo6ojLuLUHgibllggEbfiaX0KF5YTrN9pP2iaGGCQezibx1fzKicPCE2XQLq2fNNc3Fc8%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"9\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">研究人员提出，这种「局部视角」导致了严重的效率低下。通过系统</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;2D 探测接口</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，研究团队揭示了并行推理的三大底层动态特征：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p data-path-to-node=\"10,0,0\" style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><b data-path-to-node=\"10,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">非单调缩放</span></span></b><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">准确率并非随着算力投入单调增加，而是取决于「宽度」与「深度」的精细平衡（Figure (a)）。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-path-to-node=\"10,1,0\" style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><b data-path-to-node=\"10,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">路径长度不均</span></span></b><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">并行分支的生成长度差异极大，计算资源往往被少数「长尾」路径占据（Figure (b)）。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-path-to-node=\"10,2,0\" style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><b data-path-to-node=\"10,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">共识提早稳定</span></span></b><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">全局共识往往在所有分支结束前就已经达成（平均共识达成率仅为 0.31）（Figure (c)）。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"11\" style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><b data-path-to-node=\"11\" data-index-in-node=\"0\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">技术突破：基于全局信号的</span></span></b></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"11\" style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><b data-path-to-node=\"11\" data-index-in-node=\"0\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">「外科手术式」 2D Budget Control</span></span></b></p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\">即插即用：Parallel-Probe 是一种模型无关的方法，可直接适配各种现成的开源或闭源大语言模型。</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-height=\"482\" data-imgfileid=\"503535790\" data-ratio=\"0.2972222222222222\" data-width=\"1620\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=db09e18f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F5L8bhP5dIqFTAgc4hjEoQRFb9jnecpo4Jso8BZV9bqskeGibEUC36AgRlnWTDPJskicaawKH11DqeYeZ6VicP3jglRkGLqJ3gtBIC0ibDsbFjFg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"12\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">针对上述发现，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">Parallel-Probe&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">采用了一种 Training-Free 的轻量级控制器，通过两个核心机制优化同时从宽度和深度优化在线并行思考：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p data-path-to-node=\"13,0,0\" style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><b data-path-to-node=\"13,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">基于共识的早期停止（Consensus-based Early Stopping）</span></span></b><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">该机制周期性地从各分支中提取中间结果。一旦探测到全局多数答案在连续几个周期内保持稳定，控制器将直接终止整组推理，避免后续冗余步骤。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <ul style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p data-path-to-node=\"13,1,0\" style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><b data-path-to-node=\"13,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">基于偏差的分支剪枝（Deviation-based Branch Pruning）</span></span></b><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">实时监控每一条路径。如果某条路径显著偏离了当前的全局大趋势（即出现异常），系统会果断对其进行「剔除」，将资源倾注在更有潜力的路径上。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"14\" style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><b data-path-to-node=\"14\" data-index-in-node=\"0\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">实验结果：刷新帕累托前</span></span></b></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"14\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><b data-path-to-node=\"14\" data-index-in-node=\"0\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">沿</span></span></b><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">研究团队在</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;Qwen3&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">系列模型（0.6B 至 8B）上进行了广泛测试，涵盖了 AIME 2024/2025 和 HMMT 2025 等高难度竞赛题库。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-height=\"816\" data-imgfileid=\"503535791\" data-ratio=\"0.47962962962962963\" data-width=\"1700\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=47f60675&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F5L8bhP5dIqHsc0gg1KAYicAucnO17qFV5Ujz6q4cQqFMpWNia8XMUSRq4svibU6Q4DDib1YX61nhytSS2guu7EFdDCerVjJRfKBsFyFE5ib8Ol1E%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"15\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">实验结果表明，Parallel-Probe 在性能、成本效率和延迟效率之间建立了更优的平衡点，系统性地优于现有的 ESC 和 SC 等基准方法。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"16\" style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><b data-path-to-node=\"16\" data-index-in-node=\"0\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">基础设施贡献：SCOUT 测试床</span></span></b></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"16\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">为了推动该领域的持续研究，团队还推出了</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;SCOUT</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">（顺序与并发离线利用测试床）。该平台实现了推理生成与控制策略的解耦，允许开发者在极低开销下模拟各种缩放策略，极大提升了测试效率。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-height=\"1320\" data-imgfileid=\"503535792\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-width=\"2642\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e99543f6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F5L8bhP5dIqGQYxEIWOc6j7w3NZAPVeT1cfKrP4hMwCmdoicsSl7S7MQA3kZyx02enicRPs8iaDicWJYr0DFO4x4ibWicoVf220vSq0UAIxiakFlxGQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"17\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><b data-path-to-node=\"17\" data-index-in-node=\"0\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">代码及 Online Judge 平台已开源：</span></span></b></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p data-path-to-node=\"17\" style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">GitHub：</span></span>\n     <response-element ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\">\n      <link-block><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\"><a href=\"https://github.com/zhengkid/Parallel-Probe\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/zhengkid/Parallel-Probe</a></span></span></link-block>\n     </response-element></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-path-to-node=\"17\" style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">平台：Efficient Reasoning Online Judge</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"18\" style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><b data-path-to-node=\"18\" data-index-in-node=\"0\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">本文作者</span></span></b></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;text-align:justify;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">郑童</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;text-align:justify;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，马里兰大学计算机科学系二年级博士生，研究方向聚焦于&nbsp;</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;text-align:justify;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">Reasoning</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;text-align:justify;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">尤其是&nbsp;</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;text-align:justify;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">Parallel Thinking（并行思考）</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;text-align:justify;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。他的研究关注如何打破传统顺序推理在效率与鲁棒性上的瓶颈，使大语言模型能够以更结构化、更高效的方式进行并行推理。代表性工作包括</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;text-align:justify;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">Parallel-R1</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;text-align:justify;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，该工作首次提出基于强化学习的框架，在真实世界推理任务中</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;text-align:justify;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">自适应地激励并行思考行为</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;text-align:justify;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">；以及&nbsp;</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;text-align:justify;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">MoT（Mixture of Thoughts）</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;text-align:justify;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，系统性地构建多推理模态的并行思考机制，在训练与推理阶段统一整合自然语言、代码与符号推理等不同模态，从而实现更高效、更具表达力的并行推理。</span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Parallel-Probe 是一种无需训练的并行推理控制算法，通过 2D 探测技术实现早期停止和分支剪枝，显著提升大模型并行思考的效率并降低成本。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Parallel-Probe 是一种无需训练的并行推理控制算法，通过 2D 探测技术实现早期停止和分支剪枝，显著提升大模型并行思考的效率并降低成本。",
  "summary": "本文介绍了由马里兰大学、圣路易斯华盛顿大学等机构联合提出的 Parallel-Probe 研究。针对当前大模型在并行推理（Parallel Thinking）中存在的“无效计算”和“长尾路径占据资源”等痛点，研究团队通过 2D Probing 揭示了并行推理的动态特征，发现全局共识往往在所有分支结束前就已达成。Parallel-Probe 引入了基于共识的早期停止和基于偏差的分支剪枝两大核心机制，在不损失准确率的前提下，将推理延迟降低了 35.8%，Token 成本降低了 25.8%。此外，团队还推出了 SCOUT 测试床，实现了推理生成与控制策略的解耦，为该领域的后续研究提供了高效的基础设施。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "识别并行推理中的无效计算与资源浪费瓶颈。",
      "explanation": "研究发现并行推理中各分支彼此独立，导致系统必须等待所有分支完成，而全局共识往往在长尾路径结束前就已稳定，造成了严重的计算资源浪费。"
    },
    {
      "point": "提出无需训练的 Parallel-Probe 轻量级控制算法。",
      "explanation": "该算法作为一种模型无关的即插即用方案，通过 2D 探测接口系统性地刻画在线推理的全局动态，无需对原模型进行微调即可实现高效控制。"
    },
    {
      "point": "通过早期停止与分支剪枝实现“外科手术式”预算控制。",
      "explanation": "机制包括周期性监控全局共识并在稳定后提前终止推理，以及实时剔除显著偏离全局趋势的异常路径，从而在宽度和深度上同时优化推理预算。"
    },
    {
      "point": "在保持准确率的同时显著刷新了推理性能的帕累托前沿。",
      "explanation": "实验证明该方法在 AIME 等高难度竞赛题库上表现优异，不仅大幅降低了延迟和 Token 成本，还系统性地优于现有的多数投票（SC）等基准方法。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "并行推理并非一个‘算得越多越好’的过程：全局共识往往在所有分支结束之前就已提前稳定，而少数冗长的长尾路径却持续占据大量计算资源。",
    "Parallel-Probe 是一种模型无关的方法，可直接适配各种现成的开源或闭源大语言模型。",
    "一旦探测到全局多数答案在连续几个周期内保持稳定，控制器将直接终止整组推理，避免后续冗余步骤。",
    "该研究首先通过引入 2D Probing，对 online 并行推理过程中的全局动态性进行了系统性刻画。"
